HEADWORD: Photochemical
<hw>Pho`to*chem"ic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Photo-</ets> + <ets>chemical</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to chemical changes produced by light; <as>as, the
<ex>photochemical</ex> changes of the visual purple of the
retina</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

